      <title>激进对冲基金因秘密向研究人员付款而被罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/activist-hedge-fund-punished-for-secret-payments-to-researcher</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国对激进卖空者的全面调查首次产生了令人瞩目的惩罚，同时也让人们罕见地看到了看跌研究人员与对冲基金之间有争议的合作，这些对冲基金对公司进行了大举押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/activist-hedge-fund-punished-for-secret-payments-to-researcher</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 01:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国原油、汽油库存增加，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-12</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府数据显示原油库存增加，油价收窄涨幅，跌至每桶 79 美元以下。随着全球最大经济体通胀放缓幅度超过预期，油价触底。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-12</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 23:25:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
